{"tid":1150014,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"豬，全部都死豬","createTime":"2019-05-11T14:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-11T15:18:32.000Z","uid":252957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d40b22ca1cb3aa878668bcadd7d4410c47aa8ea3","tid":1150014,"uid":252957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T14:02:33.000Z","msg":"政府昨晚（10日）公布，在上水屠房一個活豬樣本驗出非洲豬瘟病毒，宣布要撲殺屠場內的6000隻活豬。活豬業界今日（11日）與食衛局長陳肇始見面，商討對策，鮮肉大聯盟理事凌偉業表示，業界一直支持若證實現時屠房內的6000隻豬若有問題就撲殺。他表示，知道當局已在這批活豬中找了樣本化驗，但一直不公布結果。他表示，業界會就當局撲殺活豬的決定提出司法覆核，業界今晚亦會回到上水屠房一直留守，保護自己的財產（活豬）。<br />\n<br />\n凌偉業說，會上沒有談過賠償問題。他重申，業界已不斷釋出善意、給出方向及讓步，但所提供意見全不獲政府接納，政府亦沒有提出何方案。他說，政府不斷說豬瘟不會人傳人、食用無問題，但要「殺晒所有豬」，是不科學。業界最關心，中國已成非洲豬瘟疫區，根本無法百分百保證來自疫區的豬無問題，若驗出豬瘟病毒成為常態應該如何處理，政府並無提出任何方案。他說，談判已經破裂。<br />\n<br />\n凌偉業表示，業界只想保護應有的權利，希望市民可以體諒。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190511/s00001/1557582344073/%E3%80%90%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E8%B1%AC%E7%98%9F%E3%80%91%E6%B4%BB%E8%B1%AC%E6%A5%AD%E6%93%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A-%E7%95%99%E5%AE%88%E5%B1%A0%E6%88%BF%E9%98%BB%E6%92%B2%E6%AE%BA%E6%B4%BB%E8%B1%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190511%2Fs00001%2F1557582344073%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E7%2598%259F%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A-%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%2588%25E5%25B1%25A0%25E6%2588%25BF%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%2592%25B2%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E8%25B1%25AC&d=0a%2BBnfQRLGMOm4peNIjNWxmJq4DTS581XL85RX03pBc%3D&h=5a4054e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20190511%2Fs00001%2F1557582344073%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E7%2598%259F%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%25B3%2595%25E8%25A6%2586%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A-%25E7%2595%2599%25E5%25AE%2588%25E5%25B1%25A0%25E6%2588%25BF%25E9%2598%25BB%25E6%2592%25B2%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E8%25B1%25AC&h=14529841\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20190511/s00001/1557582344073/%E3%80%90%E9%9D%9E%E6%B4%B2%E8%B1%AC%E7%98%9F%E3%80%91%E6%B4%BB%E8%B1%AC%E6%A5%AD%E6%93%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%B3%95%E8%A6%86%E6%A0%B8%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A-%E7%95%99%E5%AE%88%E5%B1%A0%E6%88%BF%E9%98%BB%E6%92%B2%E6%AE%BA%E6%B4%BB%E8%B1%AC</a>"},{"pid":"92ec7ea374c06d6953809cefed437972e0512e6f","tid":1150014,"uid":15815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-11T15:18:32.000Z","msg":"局長快d出黎講<br />\n我日日都食豬，大家唔好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}